  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1330624/" class="title-link">张岱对豆瓣的看法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1330624"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2083360/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2083360-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2083360/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">bukeyi333</span>
    </a>  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-19"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-19 21:25:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1330624_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  豆瓣上一无可看，止可看看上豆瓣之人。看豆瓣上之人，以五类看之：其一，叠床架屋，千卷百城，知交友邻，声光相乱，名为看书而实不见书者，看之。其一，亦文亦雅，闺秀名娃，携及童娈，语笑杂之，倚坐前屏，左右顾眄，身在书中而实不看书者，看之。其一，亦读亦批评，名妓闲僧...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1330624/#comments">(23回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">149有用 / 7没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中华书局1989版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
